                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span>R&D Engineer</span>
                                <span class="badge">₹7-20 LPA</span>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Job Outlook</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>The demand for mechanical engineers in India is projected to grow by 9% through 2030, with over 25,000 new positions annually.</p>
                        <div class="growth-sectors">
                            <span class="text-success">Growth Sectors:</span>
